query:
SELECT EXISTS(
                SELECT 1
                FROM app
                WHERE
                    (
                        app.workspaced_route IS FALSE
                        AND app.custom_path = $1
                        AND ($2::TEXT IS NULL OR app.workspace_id = $2)
                    )
                    OR (
                        app.workspaced_route IS TRUE
                        AND app.workspace_id = $3
                        AND app.custom_path = $4
                    )
            )
